                            <comment id="228120" author="srcc" created="Fri, 18 May 2018 03:17:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Peter, looking forward to the release.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Meanwhile, it seems like 2.10.4 RC1 fixes the problem, so we&apos;re good for now.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks again,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Kilian&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="228113" author="pjones" created="Thu, 17 May 2018 23:07:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Testing is in progress. The exact release date will depend on whether any serious issues are found but we are certainly aiming to have this release available ASAP.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="228112" author="srcc" created="Thu, 17 May 2018 22:36:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;And also, what&apos;s the current estimated release date for 2.10.4?&lt;/p&gt;

